@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Validación contra PostgreSQL
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promo/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"code":"DB-FIXED20","orderId":"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001"}

### Cálculo fixed: descuento esperado 20
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promo/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{"code":"DB-FIXED20","orderId":"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001"}

### Cálculo percent: 15% de 200, descuento esperado 30
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promo/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{"code":"DB-PERCENT15","orderId":"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002"}

### Cálculo tiered desordenado: 7 órdenes, descuento esperado 15
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promo/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{"code":"DB-TIERED","orderId":"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003"}

### Aplicación con estado de pago explícito; repetir para probar duplicidad
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promo/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{"code":"DB-PERCENT15","orderId":"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002","isPaid":false}
